  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In general, `clock.Set` is discouraged other than start of test _before_ you pass it to anything.\n\nAlso, Quartz mocks are not really designed for integration tests where you have a whole lot of things calling into the clock with different intervals.",
